# Inventory Management System (Office)

# User 
   - id  [PK]
   - username  [char]
   - password  [char]
   - Email  [email]
   - phone_number [char]
   - address   [char]

# Department
   - id  [PK]
   - name   [char]  -HR

# ProductCategory
   - id  [PK]
   - name   [char] - stat

# Products
   - id  [PK]
   - name   [char]  - pen
   - description  [char/text]
   - stock  [int]
   - ProductCategory [Foreign Key]
   - Department   [Foreign Key]  

# Supplier
   - id  [PK]
   - name   [char]

# Purchase
   - id  [PK]
   - Product   [Foreign Key]
   - quantity  [int]
   - Price  [float]
   - Supplier  [FK]